#: _posts/2023-12-04-testing-quarkus-with-citrus.adoc
msgid "Quarkus mail service"
msgstr ""

#: _posts/2023-12-04-testing-quarkus-with-citrus.adoc
msgid "For the test Citrus starts an SMTP mail server that is able to accept the mail messages sent by Quarkus."
msgstr ""

